name: pymkl
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "0.0.3" %}

package:
  name: pymkl
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/p/pyMKL/pyMKL-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 5a24f63f510007d908506c88aa5b6b720a0d9201b8222d14805aca1f771b6afa

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - python
    - pip
  run:
    - python
    - future
    - numpy >=1.7
    - scipy >=0.13
    - mkl

test:
  imports:
    - pyMKL

about:
  home: https://github.com/dwfmarchant/pyMKL
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: "Python wrapper of Intel MKL routines"

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - lheagy
